Name:           @PROJECT_NAME@
Version:        @PROJECT_VERSION@
Release:        1%{?dist}
Summary:        @PROJECT_DESCRIPTION@

License:        BSD
URL:            http://www.kytok.org.ua/
Group:          Applications/System
Packager:       @PROJECT_MAINTAINER@ <@PROJECT_MAINTAINER_EMAIL@>

